Then you start thinking, okay,
but Charles was not here.

41:18.142 --> 41:19.408
He wasn't at Waverly.

41:19.410 --> 41:22.144
-Right. Right, right, right.
-John was.

41:22.146 --> 41:24.280
And we think John
has just been

41:24.282 --> 41:27.716
harboring that anger
and that resentment.

41:27.718 --> 41:30.019
You know, he's not someone
you can just crossover

41:30.021 --> 41:32.155
and so it's scary --
-He's probably trying to --

41:32.157 --> 41:34.890
been trying to get through
for quite awhile.

41:34.892 --> 41:36.426
Yes, and nobody knew
the story, though.

41:36.428 --> 41:39.562
Making me feel --
you can feel that sadness.

41:39.564 --> 41:43.366
Yeah. As far as John goes on
the fourth floor, he's angry.

41:43.368 --> 41:46.970
We just recommend, when you
have investigators come in,

41:46.972 --> 41:49.105
you make them aware of him.

41:49.107 --> 41:51.574
The more people go up there
and talk to him,

41:51.576 --> 41:54.243
and tell him that they're
sympathetic to him, I think --

41:54.245 --> 41:56.111
-Maybe he can let go.
-Exactly.

41:56.113 --> 41:57.313
I'll try to help him.

41:57.315 --> 41:59.115
-Yeah.
-That really does help a lot.

41:59.117 --> 42:01.450
I mean, again,
that wasn't necessarily,

42:01.452 --> 42:03.319
wasn't our main focus
when we got here,

42:03.321 --> 42:04.620
but it became that.

42:04.622 --> 42:05.988
It really became that.

42:05.990 --> 42:08.390
Well, they made sure
that that was your focus.

42:08.392 --> 42:10.526
-Yeah, they did.
-Yeah. They actually did.

42:10.528 --> 42:12.328
They probably knew
he needed it most.

42:12.330 --> 42:15.198
-He'll let go one day.
-Yes.

42:15.200 --> 42:18.133
BRUNI: This is the exact reason
Adam and I are so adamant

42:18.135 --> 42:21.871
about identifying the spirits
responsible for a haunt.

42:21.873 --> 42:24.340
Their name helps us
tell their story

42:24.342 --> 42:27.010
and in a way,
makes them human again.

42:27.012 --> 42:30.079
♪♪
